headline: Regional Banking Sector Near a Critical Inflection Point
summary: Regional banks are nearing a major level, with the KRE ETF consolidating just below resistance at $70, setting up a potential breakout or double top scenario.

headline: Largest U.S. Bank Deals Enjoying Fast Closing Timelines
summary: Four transactions involving bank targets with over $25 billion in assets were announced in 2025, marking the first deals of that size since 2022. Read more here.
